description: Byggmästare Anders J Ahlström Holding AB engages in the acquisition, management, and development of real properties. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 398 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-12-22. Through its subsidiaries, the Company is engaged in renting and acquiring residential rental properties built within the framework of the Million Programme in the Botkyrka vicinity of Greater Stockholm. The firm operates Byggmastara Anders J Ahlstrom Fastighets AB as a wholly-owned subsidiary.
